title: Kendall Jenner returns to LA after confusing fans with curvy bikini selfie that rivalled sister Kylie
text:
Kendall Jenner returns to LA after confusing fans with curvy bikini selfie that rivalled sister Kylie Fans were confused if the bikini snap showed Kendall or Kylie’s body Share Get daily updates directly to your inbox + Subscribe Could not subscribe, try again later Invalid Email 
Kendall Jenner and Kylie Jenner might be sisters – but their looks are poles apart. 
Kendall, 21, is the supermodel favouring a natural look while her younger sister Kylie, 19, is the curvy Kim Kardashian in the making. 
So Kendall surprised fans when she shared a black and white selfie flaunting curves to rival her sister. 
The model posed in a strapless black bikini top and high leg bikini bottoms – showing off her shapely hips. Kendall Jenner kept her head down as she arrived at LAX airport (Photo: Rex Features) Kendall Jenner flaunts her curves in a black bikini (Photo: Instagram) 
“Cool, now I need a vaca (sic),” she commented on the stunning selfie shared with her 75.7m Instagram followers. 
But fans were quick to comment on how different Kendall’s body shape looked. 
“When did her body get like that?” one fan asked. She sparked a lot of talk over her body with the Instagram post (Photo: Rex Features) Fans wondered if the selfie was actually of Kylie Jenner (Photo: Instagram) 
“Is that her body or Kylie?” another fan commented, confusing Kendall with her sister. 
While others accused the model of “editing” her selfie. 
“That's Photoshop Kenny you don't have that curves (sic),” another fan wrote. Kendall wore a slouchy grey tracksuit (Photo: Rex Features) 
But returning home to LA from Paris where she walked in the Chanel show, Kendall ignored the furore caused by her revealing snap. 
As she touched down at LAX Airport she kept her head down and kept her face hidden with dark sunglasses. 
The jet-setting model wore slouchy grey jogging bottoms and a matching T-shirt with a pair of white trainers. 
She added a touch of high-fashion glamour with a camel toned fur jacket. Like us on Facebook
